<p>The following SFX were released under the <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/">Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 Unported license</a> on <a href="https://freesound.org">freesound.org</a>:</p>

<ul>
<li><em><a href="http://freesound.org/people/Benboncan/sounds/103628/">large-anvil-steel-hammer</a></em> by <a href="http://freesound.org/people/benboncan">benboncan</a> </li>
<li><em><a href="http://freesound.org/people/primeval_polypod/sounds/160596/">jets-low-pass</a></em> by <a href="http://freesound.org/people/primeval-polypod">primeval-polypod</a></li>
</ul>

<p>Original music and SFX by James P. McQuoid is licensed under the <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/">Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 Unported license</a>.</p>


<h3 style="color: #555555;">Software</h3>
<em>Script:</em> gedit, Piratepad, TextPlay (command line fountain renderer), Trelby (dedicated screenwriting application)<br />
<em>Sound recording:</em> Audacity (voice), Ardour (music)<br />
<em>Story boards:</em> Krita<br />
<em>Vector Mockups:</em> Inkscape<br />
<em>Visuals, animation, rendering, editing, sound editing:</em> Blender<br />
<em>webm encoding:</em> Transmageddon (first batch), Pitivi (second batch)</span>
        </div>
    

                             </div>
